TurtleSport needs :
-----------------------
Java 1.7 or > (see http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp)

Java
--------------
if java is not installed. On ubuntu and mint :

sudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/java
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install oracle-java7-installer

For more information : http://www.webupd8.org/2012/01/install-oracle-java-jdk-7-in-ubuntu-via.html

Run TurtleSport
----------------------------------
turtlesport
or in a console : java -jar turtlesport.jar
